n4. Tap field again - focus listener selects ALL text ("not-a-url")\n5. Type "ht
tp://10.0.2.2:3001/api/v1" - replaces selected text\n6. Error disappears\n7. Sav
e succeeds\n\nLet me update the flow and test again.',
